    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 获批增持股份以资助比特币购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/microstrategy-share-increase-approved-to-fund-bitcoin-purchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 股东投票决定将授权 A 类普通股数量增加 30 倍，以帮助为公司购买比特币提供资金。]]></description>
