    <item>
      <title>价值 3 亿美元的俄罗斯超级游艇命运悬而未决，美国仍在审理中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/fate-of-300-million-russian-superyacht-is-subject-of-us-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府周二向法庭提起诉讼，称一名受到制裁的亿万富翁才是其在 2022 年扣押的一艘超级游艇的真正主人，目前美国政府正在追查乌克兰战争背后富有的俄罗斯人的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/fate-of-300-million-russian-superyacht-is-subject-of-us-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:32:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师下调 iPhone 风险，苹果 1 月份业绩更差</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/apple-s-tough-january-worsens-as-analysts-cut-on-iphone-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 遭到两名分析师的评级下调，这一最新迹象表明，由于人工智能未能发挥预期的增长催化剂的作用，iPhone 销售疲软正成为投资者日益担心的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/apple-s-tough-january-worsens-as-analysts-cut-on-iphone-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:47:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
